.TH h5i 1  "h5i 0.2.8" 
.SH NAME
h5i \- Auditable workspaces for AI coding agents
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBh5i\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Auditable workspaces for AI coding agents
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
h5i\-init(1)
Initialize the h5i sidecar in the current repository
.TP
h5i\-completion(1)
Generate a shell completion script (bash, zsh, fish, ...); e.g. `h5i completion bash > /etc/bash_completion.d/h5i`
.TP
h5i\-man(1)
Generate the roff man page from the CLI definition (so it never drifts from the actual commands); e.g. `h5i man > man/man1/h5i.1`
.TP
h5i\-capture(1)
Record provenance \(em commit, memory snapshot. Run `h5i capture \-\-help` for the verb table with runnable examples
.TP
h5i\-recall(1)
Read AI history \(em log, blame, diff, context, notes, memory, recap, resume. Run `h5i recall \-\-help` for the verb table
.TP
h5i\-audit(1)
Assess risk \(em review\-rank, prompt\-injection scan, compliance, policy, vibe. Run `h5i audit \-\-help` for the verb table
.TP
h5i\-share(1)
Publish \(em push, pull, and post a sticky GitHub PR comment with AI provenance. Run `h5i share \-\-help` for the verb table
.TP
h5i\-env(1)
Isolated agent environments \(em worktree + sandbox + provenance (docs/environments\-design.md). create/run/diff/propose/apply lifecycle
.TP
h5i\-team(1)
Agent teams \(em phased evidence publication over existing h5i envs
.TP
h5i\-resolve(1)
Resolve branch conflicts using CRDT\-based semantic merging
.TP
h5i\-serve(1)
Launch the h5i web dashboard in your browser
.TP
h5i\-hook(1)
Manage agent hook setup for automatic prompt capture and context tracing. Run `h5i hook setup` to print install instructions
.TP
h5i\-resume(1)
Generate a structured handoff briefing to resume an AI session
.TP
h5i\-mcp(1)
Start the h5i MCP (Model Context Protocol) server on stdio
.TP
h5i\-doctor(1)
Validate and repair h5i sidecar storage and refs
.TP
h5i\-policy(1)
Manage governance policy for AI\-assisted commits (.h5i/policy.toml)
.TP
h5i\-msg(1)
Agent radio \(em cross\-agent messaging over a shareable Git ref
.TP
h5i\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
