.SH "H5I MSG RISK"
i5h RISK: flag a hazard the recipient should inspect. h5i msg risk --focus src/auth.rs --priority high all auth cache crosses requests
.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.SS SYNOPSIS
\fBrisk\fR [\fB\-\-from\fR] [\fB\-\-branch\fR] [\fB\-\-focus\fR] [\fB\-\-priority\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fITO\fR> <\fIBODY\fR> 
.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.SS OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-from\fR \fI<FROM>\fR

.TP
\fB\-\-branch\fR \fI<BRANCH>\fR
Git branch this risk relates to (default: current branch; pass "" to leave untagged)
.TP
\fB\-\-focus\fR \fI<FOCUS>\fR

.TP
\fB\-\-priority\fR \fI<PRIORITY>\fR
low | normal | high | urgent
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fITO\fR>

.TP
<\fIBODY\fR>

.SH "H5I MSG HANDOFF"
i5h HANDOFF: transfer task ownership/context to another agent. h5i msg handoff --branch auth --context auth reviewer please take expiry work
.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
