Git branch being handed off (default: current branch; pass "" to leave untagged)
.TP
\fB\-\-context\fR \fI<CONTEXT>\fR
h5i context branch relevant to the handoff
.TP
\fB\-\-focus\fR \fI<FOCUS>\fR

.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fITO\fR>

.TP
<\fIBODY\fR>

